  <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-6">Medical Disclaimer</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-6 mb-8">
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-2">
          ⚠️ Important: This Site Does Not Provide Medical Advice
        </p>
        <p class="text-yellow-800">
          CompareMensCare.com is an informational comparison website only.
          Always consult with a qualified healthcare professional before making any health decisions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2>No Doctor-Patient Relationship</h2>
      <p>
        The information provided on CompareMensCare.com is for educational and comparison purposes only
        and does not constitute medical advice. Reading our content or using our comparison tools does
        not create a doctor-patient relationship between you and CompareMensCare.com, its owners,
        authors, or any affiliated healthcare providers.
      </p>

      <h2>Consult Your Doctor</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Always seek the advice of your physician or other qualified health provider</strong>
        with any questions you may have regarding a medical condition or treatment. Never disregard
        professional medical advice or delay in seeking it because of something you have read on
        CompareMensCare.com.
      </p>

      <h2>Medical Emergencies</h2>
      <p>
        If you think you may have a medical emergency, call your doctor, go to the emergency department,
        or call 911 (in the United States) immediately. CompareMensCare.com does not recommend or
        endorse any specific tests, physicians, products, procedures, opinions, or other information
        that may be mentioned on the site.
      </p>

      <h2>Information Accuracy</h2>
      <p>
        While we strive to provide accurate, up-to-date information, we make no representations or
        warranties about the completeness, accuracy, reliability, suitability, or availability of
        the information, products, services, or related graphics contained on the website for any purpose.
      </p>
      <p>
        Pricing, service availability, and medication options can change frequently. We update our
        content regularly, but there may be delays. Always verify current information directly with
        the healthcare providers we review.
      </p>

      <h2>Medication Information</h2>
      <p>
        Information about medications, including potential side effects, contraindications, and
        drug interactions, is provided for educational purposes only. This information is not
        exhaustive and should not replace the prescribing information, medical consultation, or
        advice of a licensed healthcare professional.
      </p>

      <h3>Important Medication Safety Notes:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>All medications can have side effects</li>
        <li>ED medications are contraindicated with nitrates and certain heart conditions</li>
        <li>Hair loss medications may affect prostate health markers</li>
        <li>Testosterone therapy requires regular monitoring</li>
        <li>Mental health medications require professional supervision</li>
        <li>Always disclose your complete medical history and current medications to your provider</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        The telehealth services we review are independent third-party providers. CompareMensCare.com
        does not provide medical services and is not responsible for the medical care, advice, or
        treatment provided by any of the companies we review.
      </p>
      <p>
        When you use our affiliate links to access these services, you will be subject to their own
        terms of service, privacy policies, and medical practices. We encourage you to review each
        provider's policies before using their services.
      </p>

      <h2>No Guarantees of Results</h2>
      <p>
        Individual results may vary. The effectiveness of any treatment depends on many factors
        including the individual's specific condition, overall health, adherence to treatment,
        and other variables. We make no guarantees about the results you may or may not experience
        from any treatment or provider.
      </p>

      <h2>Medical Review</h2>
      <p>
        While some of our content is reviewed by medical professionals, this review is for accuracy
        and educational purposes only. It does not constitute medical advice specific to your situation.
        Medical reviewers are not providing personal medical care or treatment recommendations.
      </p>

      <h2>Mental Health Resources</h2>
      <p>
        If you are experiencing a mental health crisis, please contact:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>National Suicide Prevention Lifeline:</strong> 988 (U.S.)</li>
        <li><strong>Crisis Text Line:</strong> Text HOME to 741741 (U.S.)</li>
        <li><strong>Emergency Services:</strong> 911 (U.S.)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Updates to This Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to modify this medical disclaimer at any time. Changes will be
        effective immediately upon posting to the website. Your continued use of the site
        after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the new disclaimer.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this medical disclaimer, please contact us at the email
        address provided on our contact page.
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
        <strong>Last updated:</strong> January 15, 2025
      </p>
    </div>
